#O  VecToString( <vec> ) . . . . . . . . write vector as s string
##
##  <#GAPDoc Label="VecToString">
##  <ManSection>
##  <Meth Name="VecToString" Arg="[B,] vec"/>
##
##  <Description>
##  Writes a FFE verctor or matrix as string or list of strings using the given
